weave, vi.
 es: tejer, vi.| hilar, vtr.| entrelazar, vtr.| zigzaguearm vi.| serpentear, vi.| tejido, n.| (pelo) postizo n.|
 to lace together (threads, strands, etc.) so as to form a fabric.
 to form by weaving.
 (of a spider or similar small creature) to spin (a web or cocoon).
 to combine into a connected whole.
 to (cause to) move by winding or zigzagging.
 a pattern of or method for weaving.